All Implemented Interfaces:
ContextEnabled, Mojo
@Mojo(name="dependencies",
      requiresDependencyResolution=TEST)
public class PlayDependenciesMojo
extends AbstractDependencyProcessingPlayMojo

Extract project dependencies to "lib" and "modules" directories. It's like Play! framework's "dependencies" command, but uses Maven dependencies, instead of "conf/dependencies.yml" file.

Since:
1.0.0
Author:
Grzegorz Slowikowski
